e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T07:44:16.000Z","msg":"過橋抽板 慣啦"},{"pid":"85ce8a7ef58f61266bed30bcf3d132437f06bae2","tid":1173412,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T07:45:13.000Z","msg":"Link?"},{"pid":"85b9ea870d5db98cf36c2602dc2a89c926b55e58","tid":1173412,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T07:45:30.000Z","msg":"又係陸頌雄呢條戇鳩仔"},{"pid":"0faa0df3027c404f03b433db6e0b9be5dbdd87a9","tid":1173412,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T07:47:27.000Z","msg":"選舉年，又要做大龍鳳刷存在感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed1cdf703fdeffd100cde63070ad5cf0a87d34f","tid":1173412,"uid":23120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T07:48:09.000Z","msg":"陸頌雄的父親<strong>陸德成</strong>曾於1967年六七暴動期間，在太古船塢工會會所被捕，被控<strong>非法集會入獄</strong>。陸頌雄曾就讀中華基督教會何福堂書院以及於香港專業進修學校修讀社會工作高級文憑，之後再進一步修讀香港公開大學社會科學課程，但<strong>英語水平極差</strong>。 <br />\n政治生涯[編輯]<br />\n在2003年區議會選舉中，陸頌雄代表民建聯在新成立的天恆選區當選，其後代表工聯會，一直在天恆選區連任至今[4]。2016年香港立法會選舉時，陸頌雄代表工聯會在無競爭之下自動當選成為勞工界功能界別議員。他於當議員之前曾在廣華醫院任<strong>註冊護士學生</strong>以及在<strong>友邦保險任職理財顧問</strong>。另外，又在陳有海徐帆議員辦事處擔任議員助理。他是香港工會聯合會元朗綜合服務中心的助理主任。 <br />\n2018年9月，陸頌雄會面英國議會跨黨派中國小組，並與前港督彭定康合照[5]。亦有合照被陸頌雄改圖，將英國議員和泛民主派議員全部合成為彭定康的樣貌[6]"},{"pid":"23991f0c658870cb68e06994e54fc5ce4304cef6","tid":1173412,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:00:01.000Z","msg":"工聯狗 又趕絕基層<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29991cdeaf049509a27fcaa079130ae3efa376e5","tid":1173412,"uid":212509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85b9ea870d5db98cf36c2602dc2a89c926b55e58","tid":1173412,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T07:45:30.000Z","msg":"又係陸頌雄呢條戇鳩仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:09:39.000Z","msg":"佢真係好想連任 唔知可以deal到咩位呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46828e4471389067ace4c71867b29c2fd7b72866","tid":1173412,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29991cdeaf049509a27fcaa079130ae3efa376e5","tid":1173412,"uid":212509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85b9ea870d5db98cf36c2602dc2a89c926b55e58","tid":1173412,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T07:45:30.000Z","msg":"又係陸頌雄呢條戇鳩仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:09:39.000Z","msg":"佢真係好想連任 唔知可以deal到咩位呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:15:35.000Z","msg":"工聯會勞工界選兩次要轉直選"},{"pid":"b70c24c94e545ec45f80d270aaf884abe23d518d","tid":1173412,"uid":212509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46828e4471389067ace4c71867b29c2fd7b72866","tid":1173412,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29991cdeaf049509a27fcaa079130ae3efa376e5","tid":1173412,"uid":212509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85b9ea870d5db98cf36c2602dc2a89c926b55e58","tid":1173412,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T07:45:30.000Z","msg":"又係陸頌雄呢條戇鳩仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:09:39.000Z","msg":"佢真係好想連任 唔知可以deal到咩位呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:15:35.000Z","msg":"工聯會勞工界選兩次要轉直選"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:18:15.000Z","msg":"之前有post討論過有咩直選位可以比佢選<br />\n結果就係除非有人退位讓比佢，否則得九西或者超區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但九西本身建制冇可能夠餅派"},{"pid":"38100ec48d8578fb3d09740c2fd280ecdddae538","tid":1173412,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b70c24c94e545ec45f80d270aaf884abe23d518d","tid":1173412,"uid":212509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46828e4471389067ace4c71867b29c2fd7b72866","tid":1173412,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29991cdeaf